d you say?' he asked again, suddenly ceasing to sob. 'Home, home,' repeated the voice, and the glass radiance, taking hold of Luzhin, threw him out into the cool dusk.

Luzhin smiled. 'Home,' he said softly. 'So that's the key to the combination.'



